---
title: Easy Creamy Chicken, Bacon & Tomato Spaghetti with Parsley
description: Golden ropes of spaghetti coated in a rich, creamy tomato sauce, bacon and tender chunks of chicken. Finished with a a pinch of chilli flakes if you like a bit of heat, this is nothing short of a small bite of heaven.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/648ab6d0398e9ea23dba381d-cff45938.jpeg
